      Bangladesh opposition Bangladesh Nationalist Party leader Salauddin Quader Chowdhury, shown in an October 2013 file photo, heard a ruling Wednesday July 29, 2015 from the Supreme Court of Bangladesh upholding the death penalty for him. The ruling clears the way for his execution unless he gets presidential clemency.
      
